ta":{"text":"Hider 2"},"id":"3639e97a-6238-4b56-ad9a-9b3b3558f03f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"text":"Introduction"},"id":"78bb5a19-9d8e-4305-b394-b0732c4741bc","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Hider 2 keeps your files hidden and protected on your hard drive from real and virtual intruders. This <a href=\"/best-encryption-software\">Mac encryption software</a> is slow to decrypt, but it&#39;s easy to use overall and has strong security features.","Hider 2 is one of the few file encryption programs for Mac with a file shredder to delete your unwanted files permanently. It&#39;s easy to assume old data is gone once you&#39;ve emptied the wastebasket, but this is not the case on Macs or PCs. The file shredder overwrites your deleted files to make them unrecoverable. This encryption software also uses AES 256-bit to hide and protect your data. This algorithm is the top of the line, trusted by military and federal sources for encrypting files.","Hider has an ultra-simple interface to please techy types and newcomers alike. To add your files, you simply drag and drop them into Hider. When you open the program, you see a padlock graphic that twists as you enter your password. Once you&#39;re in Hider, your database begins with the Primary Vault. From there, you can categorize different documents in groups such as finances or passwords. Within Hider, you can create text docs related to other items in the database or notes you want to keep private. And even if you organize your protected database well, sifting through files is still a pain, so Hider lets you access your files with a quick search.","However, Hider 2 was the slowest program in our decryption tests. Although it took under seven seconds to encrypt the 134.5MB test file, we waited over 16 seconds to decrypt the same file. This may sound like small potatoes, but time matters when you need to decrypt large files. Thankfully, the test file remained roughly the same size, so you don&#39;t need extra space for your files with this software.","As with all Mac encryption software, you need to remember to lock Hider once you&#39;re done. You can also set the time for the auto-lock feature to kick in. Once you&#39;re inactive, Hider locks after your preferred time, ranging from seconds to half an hour. This software also has a password strength meter to show you how secure your chosen password is, though it doesn&#39;t have a password generator to come up with one for you.","There are visibility settings within the program for if you want to keep items within reach but keep them locked from any intruders. Ironically, though, Hider may hide too effectively. In our tests, we had trouble finding our protected files once the icon disappeared from the desktop.","In case you have questions about using Hider or run into problems, the program has the important support features. You can find answers in the FAQs page about AES-256, moving files and network protection. The software&#39;s manual is available on the website as well. For the big questions, you can contact customer support for Hider 2 via phone or the email form on the website."]},"id":"e27e3774-0c0e-475e-80b6-dcba27f5244a","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"9a99ccd9-3167-4a16-a78c-e2b702e3d169","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Hider 2 uses the toughest encryption algorithm, keeps file sizes consistent when encrypting and decrypting, and deletes unwanted items completely with its file shredder. Although it lacks speed and some features of the best Mac encryption software, Hider 2 is easy software to use to keep encrypted files on hand but conceal them from intruders."]},"id":"6c7d12ab-81b6-4777-945d-ef6b8b5ada4c","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_67616","url":"/hider-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"nicole-johnston","url":"/author/nicole-johnston","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Nicole Johnston","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"nR6fcTbvfudgncYJ